#: ckanext/comments/templates/comments/snippets/helper.html:8
msgid ""
"The commenting feature allows users to engage with dataset publishers and the"
" community by sharing feedback, suggestions, or questions directly on dataset"
" pages. Whether you want to clarify dataset details, highlight potential "
"improvements, or discuss usage scenarios, this feature provides a space for "
"collaborative discussions. Comments help enhance dataset quality and ensure "
"the information is as useful and relevant as possible. Start a conversation "
"and contribute to the ongoing improvement of open data."
msgstr ""

